Package com.fssa.cinephile.model

Class Movie

java.lang.Object
com.fssa.cinephile.model.Movie
public class Movie extends Object
The Movie class represents a movie entity in the application. It includes information about the movie's title, ID, rating, and image URL.
Author:
UtchikannaNeelakanda
